Final phase. Removes the remaining @ts-nocheck headers from the Phase 5
governance scaffolds, refreshes the top-level docs to reflect the
six-phase build, and ships a launch checklist that walks an operator
from clean checkout to production deploy.

Type safety pass:
- promotion_discipline.ts: removed @ts-nocheck. Expanded GateRequirement
  to allow boolean threshold/actual; rewrote grade comparison with an
  explicit Record<string, number> lookup so the indexer is type-safe.
- shadow_scorecard.ts: removed @ts-nocheck. Renamed interface
  ShadowScorecard -> ShadowScorecardReport to resolve the name collision
  with the class. Cast actualValue (number | boolean) to Number() in the
  reduce that computes avgPromoted/avgRejected Sharpe. Mapped the wider
  PromotionDecision union (NEEDS_EXTENSION) onto the narrower history
  entry union (EXTENDED) at recordPromotionApproval.
- trust_surface.ts: removed @ts-nocheck. Aligned the DetailedBrief and
  generateDetailedRisks return types on the source-of-truth field name
  (likelihood) used by highlightRisks().

Documentation truth pass:
- README.md: added Phase 5/6 API surfaces (governance + calibration
  schedulers, /api/slo/*) and a "Production-Readiness Build Phases"
  section that maps the seven phase branches to outcomes.
- docs/ARCHITECTURE.md: documented the scheduler + SLO endpoints and
  the SSE alert router behaviour (subscribes to Phase 5 SSE event types,
  fires fireAlert(), 60s burn-rate scanner).
- docs/OPERATOR_RUNBOOK.md: added Phase 5/6 quick-reference curls and
  the new env vars (PROMOTION_SCHEDULER_INTERVAL_MS,
  CALIBRATION_SCHEDULER_INTERVAL_MS, SSE_ALERT_ROUTER_AUTOSTART,
  SLO_SCAN_INTERVAL_MS, SLO_OBSERVATION_MAX).

Launch checklist:
- docs/LAUNCH_CHECKLIST.md (NEW): pre-flight, install + typecheck +
