+### SLOs & Alert Routing (Phase 6)
+
+- `GET  /api/slo/definitions` — Codified SLO source of truth
+- `GET  /api/slo/budgets` — Snapshot incl. burn rate per SLO
+- `GET  /api/slo/burn-rate` — Currently alerting SLOs only
